##---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Install ArcSight SmartConnector Test Alert - Replay event data for POC and Learning Labs
# Download ArcSight SmartConnector e.g. ArcSight-7.14.0.8241.0-Connector-Linux64.bin
##---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Login as Root
chmod +x ArcSight-7.14.0.8241.0-Connector-Linux64.bin
##---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Login as User/Arcsight
./ArcSight-7.14.0.8241.0-Connector-Linux64.bin
Select Test user
##---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To modify service configuration, you must be running as root 

To manually configure, log on as root and execute the following script: 

/home/arcsight/ArcSightSmartConnectors/current/bin/arcsight agentsvc -i -u user 

To manually remove the service, log on as root and execute the following script: 

/home/arcsight/ArcSightSmartConnectors/current/bin/arcsight agentsvc -r

/home/arcsight/ArcSightSmartConnectors
